# VerityMesh public-repo ignore rules.
# Keep source, schemas, fixtures, docs, and small public benchmark assets tracked.
# Keep secrets, local agent state, dependency folders, build output, caches, and
# large/generated run artifacts out of public commits.

Project_Guidelines.md

